Notes: SP's Nechuta scored career-high 34 points...WW took 5-2 lead before SP scored
next eight points and never trailed again...SP led by at least eight points
during entire second half, though its biggest lead was 62-48 with 5:27 left...
SP's sixth straight win over WW.
